postfix-h:  This help

## Postfix aliases:

 prl: postfix reload
pchk: postfix check
  ps: systemctl status postfix
 ps@: systemctl tatus postfix@-


## Postfix hash commands:

$ sudo postmap -F hash:tls_server_sni_maps
